claim.claim-text:
1. A pharmaceutical composition comprising: a therapeutically effective amount of 5-aminosalicylic acid or a pharmaceutically-acceptable salt thereof, and a therapeutically effective amount of N-acetylcysteine or a pharmaceutically-acceptable salt thereof, together disposed in a pharmaceutically-acceptable carrier;
wherein the 5-aminosalicylic acid, or a pharmaceutically-acceptable salt thereof, is present at a dose of between 1 mg/kg to 100 mg/kg; and
wherein the composition is formulated for a route of administration selected from the group consisting of oral, intrarectal, and parenteral administration.
